              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Terms & Conditions: Admission Ticket is valid for 6 months from the date of issue.Eligibility Free admission applies to children aged 2 years old and below. Child ticket applies to ages 4–12 years old. Adult ticket applies to ages 13 years old and above.Attraction Access Follow all instructions from park staff during shows and feeding sessions. Maintain a safe distance from crocodile enclosures. No outside food or drinks are allowed inside the park.Additional Information All prices are subject to change without prior notice. Tickets are non-transferable and must be used by the same person. Crocodile Adventureland Langkawi reserves the right to request additional information or documentation for verification purposes.Important Notes Entry may be rejected if guests do not comply with the stated requirements. Price differences may be charged if identification is not provided. The management reserves the right to refuse, alter, amend, delete, or add to the stated terms and conditions, or withdraw any promotion at any time without prior notice."
